Cell.Text: Look, we all have our flaws; mine is that woman can't get enough of me. | So I had this little affair going on while I was betrothed to a beautiful girl named Svidi. | Well, she finds out and she tells her brother, Wulfur. Then her brother attacks me with a knife... I mean, I had to defend myself!

Node.Caption: FFRiften02SibbiJailBranchTopic: Why are you in jail?

Node.ToolTip:

Cell.Text: Exactly! And now I have to stare at these bars for eight months. Can you believe it? | I was about to let that wench marry into the richest family in Riften, and this is how she repays me. | I'd do anything to have that whore's head on a platter. All I need to know is where she is.

Node.Caption: FFRiften02SibbiJailBranchTopic01: So you got arrested for his murder?

Cell.Text: Good, good. Just point me the right direction and I'll do the rest.

Cell.Text: Ivarstead? So close to Riften? She's an even bigger fool than I thought.

Node.Caption: FFRiften02SibbiReturnBranchTopic01: She's in Ivarstead using the name Lynly.

Cell.Text: So, the whore thinks the Black-Briar reach ends at the border of Skyrim, eh? She'll soon discover her mistake.

Node.Caption: FFRiften02SibbiReturnBranchTopic02: She's made her way east into Morrowind.

Cell.Text: [S] That's the spirit. Find her and I promise you'll be well compensated.

Node.Caption: FFRiften02SibbiJailBranchTopic03: Good luck finding her from there.

Cell.Text: She was a young woman... buxom, with long flowing black hair. | She used to sing the most lovely songs to me when we were courting. I've never heard a voice so beautiful. | All that talent will go to waste when I'm finished with her.

Node.Caption: FFRiften02SibbiSvidiBranchTopic: Do you have any information on Svidi?

Cell.Text: Mother thought I should be taught a lesson for airing the family's dirty laundry in public. | I mean, I've... taken care of many people for her in the past. What in Oblivion did she expect me to do? | Ah well. At least I have all the comforts of home during my stay. Well, except the touch of a woman of course.

Node.Caption: FFRiften02SibbiMonthsBranchTopic: You're serving only eight months for murder?

Cell.Text: [S] Well, that's just about the best news I've heard all week. | I was going to give this to whomever killed her for me, but I suppose you've earned it by bringing me this information. | This key opens one of my drop spots in the basement of the meadery. Take anything inside you like.
Cut out the middleman, eh? Shrewd, very shrewd. You sure you don't have some Black-Briar blood in you?
You idiot. You came all the way down here for that?
[S] You've done me a great service, my friend. Allow me to compensate you for the information. | This key opens one of my stashes in the basement of the meadery. Help yourself to any of its contents.
